Uttar Pradesh
Sep 13, 2014
Abduction, Child Sexual Abuse, Rape
Description:
			A 13-year-old girl was allegedly kidnapped and gang-raped by four people in Jareefnagar area here, following which two of them have been arrested, police said today.

The incident took place last night when the victim, who was sleeping on the terrace of her house, was kidnapped and raped by the four, SSP Santosh Kumar Singh said.

The accused have been identified as Amit, Muktiyaar, Bhola Pandit, and Dannu, he said.

Amit and Muktiyaar have been arrested following a complaint by the girl's father while Bhola and Dannu are absconding, police said.

